review:
I was scared of removing my impacted lower wisdom tooth since 3 years. As it was continuously paining in every 4-5 months, I got fed up and checked for any good dentist nearby. I read many reviews and found Dr. Rajeev. So I called and booked an appointment. He saw it and explained everything in detail through xray. After two days my impacted wisdom tooth was removed through surgery without pain. Healing process was quit long bcz of surgery but he was always there for any queries. Now my stitches are removed and it‚Äôs improving day by day.  

I would definitely recommend the doctor for: 
His professionalism 
Post surgery follow up
Following covid protocols
Clean office 

I am highly satisfied with the treatment. Thank you Muskan Dental & Implant Clinic.
